<section class="brand--ministry-of-justice brand__border-color organisation__brand-border-top organisation__section-wrap organisation__margin-bottom" id="what-we-do">
  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">What the Her Majesty’s Prison and Probation Service does</h2>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    
          <p></p>
<div class="govspeak">
<p>We carry out sentences given by the courts, in custody and the community, and rehabilitate people in our care through education and employment.</p>

<p><abbr title="Her Majesty’s Prison and Probation Service">HMPPS</abbr> is an executive agency, sponsored by the <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice">Ministry of Justice</a>, supported by <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations#her-majestys-prison-and-probation-service">2 agencies and public bodies</a>.</p>
</div>

          <p>
            <a href="/government/organisations/her-majestys-prison-and-probation-service/about" class="brand__color">
              Read more about what we do
            </a>
          </p>

</div>
    </div>

